reviewText: It was just as I expected except it won't play on my tv or my computer. It only plays in my car and I'm pretty bummed because I really wanted to watch it on my tv. It would have been nice to know this beforehand.
Love the Eagles my go to group
Rare among rockers, these guys are every bit as good live as they are in the studio. Nice to see Don F & Joe W playing together one last time.
Just as described and would buy again!
An oldie but goodie, for sure!
